content.raw:
Can you can the function name to `Username`? Here is the reasoning:

* The username (one word) is the thing you type in with your password, for example: bobsmith66.

* The user name (two words) is the name of the user, the user's real life name, for example: Bob Smith.
content.html:
Can you can the function name to Username? Here is the reasoning:

  • The username (one word) is the thing you type in with your password, for example: bobsmith66.

  • The user name (two words) is the name of the user, the user's real life name, for example: Bob Smith.
